        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Hmm it works for `nvim_put()` (and therefore `nvim_paste()`). Currently it passes an empty `regname`, but that may be mistaken for the unnamed register.\r\n\r\n> - `nvim_buf_set_text()`\r\n> - `nvim_buf_set_lines()`\r\n\r\nI don't think triggering `TextPut*` for these is desired. At least it's undesired for the use cases in #15136 and vim/vim#18701.",
            "created_at": "2026-05-11T22:19:49Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/39741#issuecomment-4425629373",
