        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Currently it passes an empty `regname`, but that may be mistaken for the unnamed register.\r\n\r\nI've decided to change it to pass `_` instead, as this won't conflict with the addition of future register names or be mistaken for another register (pasting from the `_` register doesn't trigger TextPut* autocommands).",
            "created_at": "2026-05-12T07:39:52Z",
